         <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">

         	<p n="01">Prosperity!</p>
         	<p n="1-3">Fourteenth <supplied reason="subaudible">year</supplied> of the victorious king Dantivikramavarman.</p>
         	<p n="4-8">Stone <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kal</foreign></supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">for</supplied> Cattima Vakilavaṉ Vīraiyar, who fell protecting the village without arm <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>aḻiyāmai</foreign></supplied> <supplied reason="explanation">for it, that is, the village</supplied>, while Malaiyaṉ <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>malaiyaṉṉār</foreign></supplied> was ruling over the Aṭaiyāṟunāṭu <supplied reason="subaudible">and</supplied> while an army was coming at once <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>orukil</foreign> = <foreign>orukāl</foreign>?</supplied> on Maṇarccuṉai <gap reason="ellipsis"/> <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>peṉṉai</foreign></supplied></p>

         </div>

